<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Lendmeyourhand</title>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>

    <!-- Le HTML5 shim, for IE6-8 support of HTML elements -->
    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
      <script src="http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <![endif]-->

    <!-- Le styles -->
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", :media => "all" %>

    <!-- Le fav and touch icons -->
    <link href="images/favicon.ico" rel="shortcut icon">
    <link href="images/apple-touch-icon.png" rel="apple-touch-icon">
    <link href="images/apple-touch-icon-72x72.png" rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="72x72">
    <link href="images/apple-touch-icon-114x114.png" rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="114x114">
  </head>
  <body>

    <div class="navbar navbar-fixed-top">
      <div class="navbar-inner">
          <div class="container">
          <a class="btn btn-navbar" data-target=".nav-collapse" data-toggle="collapse">
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          </a>
          <a class="brand" href="/hands">Lendmeyourhand</a>
          <div class="container nav-collapse">
            <ul class="nav">
              <li><%= link_to "Guess Hands", "/hands"  %></li>
              <li><%= link_to "Upload your hand", :controller => 'hands', :action => 'new'  %></li>
            </ul>
          </div><!--/.nav-collapse -->
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <% flash.each do |key, value| %>
        <div class="alert alert-block alert-<%= key == :notice ? "success" : key %>" data-dismiss="alert">
          <a class="close">Ã—</a>
          <h4 class="alert-heading"><%= key.capitalize %>:</h4>
          <%= value %>
        </div>
    <% end %>


    <div class="container">
      <div class="content">
        <div class="row">
           <div class="span9">
              <%= yield %>
            </div>
            <div class="span3">
              <div class="well sidebar-nav">
                <h3>Sidebar</h3>
                  <p> 
                    Christie's mock law trial has a section in which the parents of the murder victim are able to identify the deceased solely on the severed hand of the deceased.</p>
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    I called bullshit and said no one can identify someone just based on their hand (including myself), Christie disagrees.
                  </p>
                    <h4>The question is could you truthfully and accurately identify someone by only looking at their hand? </h4>
                  </p>              
              </div><!--/.well -->
            </div><!--/span-->
        </div><!--/row-->
      </div><!--/content-->

      <footer>
        <p>&copy; Company 2012</p>
      </footer>

    </div> <!-- /container -->

    <!-- Le javascript
    ================================================== -->
    <!-- Placed at the end of the document so the pages load faster -->
    <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>

  </body>
</html>
